lation(source);\n            // This should either compile or have a specific diagnostic\n            var diagnostics = compilation.GetDiagnostics();\n            // Just verify compilation doesn't crash\n            Assert.NotNull(diagnostics);\n        }\n    }\n}\n", "numLines": 548, "startLine": 1, "totalLines": 548}}

